{{熱力學}}
'''等焓過程'''（{{lang-en|'''isenthalpic process'''}}）是一種[[熱力學過程|熱力學過程]]，過程中的[[焓|焓]]H（或是比焓h）不變<ref>{{cite book | last = Atkins | first = Peter
| coauthors = Julio de Paula
| title = Atkin's Physical Chemistry
| url = https://archive.org/details/atkinsphysicalch00atki | publisher = Oxford University Press
| date = 2006
| location = Oxford
| isbn = 9780198700722
| page = [https://archive.org/details/atkinsphysicalch00atki/page/64 64]}}</ref>，[[真實氣體|真實氣體]]的[[焦耳-湯姆孫效應|節流過程]]就是等焓過程的一個例子。

等焓過程中，過程前的焓等於過程後的焓，焓的變化量為0。
* <math>h_1=h_2</math>
* <math>dh = 0</math>

